============================================================================
:End Note

Process called "netbsd_arm64_PROT_NONE" returns Integer:
    Return 0  Note: No access
End Process

Process called "netbsd_arm64_PROT_READ" returns Integer:
    Return 1  Note: Pages can be read
End Process

