@Performance_Hints
munmap tears down PTEs and returns physical pages to the page allocator.
Cost is O(pages) for the PTE walk. IPI shootdown to invalidate other
CPUs' TLB entries adds latency on multi-CPU systems but is amortized
over large unmaps.
